# Пользователи
## Создать нового пользователя

POST http://localhost:5000/users/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newUser@mail.net",
  "avatarPath": "lebrone1.png",
  "name": "New USer",
  "password": "123456",
  "userType": "User"
}

